VERDICT: APPROVED_WITH_COMMENTS
The diff successfully implements SDXL-family support with optional negative prompts across the image pipeline, and does so without introducing blocking regressions.

Critical findings / analysis:
- `cloudflare_ai.py`VERDICT: APPROVED_WITH_COMMENTS
